title: Jenkins and Jonez - We can't ignore Chet
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - We can't ignore Chet
description:
The guys dive into the world of vacuums, and why vacuums don't vacuum anymore. They also discuss the standstill between the Nets and Lakers, what the future may hold for Chet after one Summer League game, and the joy that is sleeping in the movies. #Herd
